Pantheon engine

A continuous reasoning loop.

⸻

One caution (important)

Running reasoning engines nonstop can create:

• runaway loops
• duplicate work
• artifact spam

So you usually add:

MAX_RUNS_PER_GOAL = 3
MIN_TIME_BETWEEN_RUNS = 1h

This keeps it stable.

